# DigitalOcean Build Ignore Patterns
# Files/directories that shouldn't trigger ML backend rebuilds

# Extension changes shouldn't trigger ML rebuild
apps/extension/**

# Frontend changes shouldn't trigger ML rebuild
apps/web/**

# Documentation changes
*.md
!services/ml-core/*.md

# Config files not affecting ML
.gitignore
.editorconfig

# Extension-specific files
apps/extension/.env.*
apps/extension/dist/
apps/extension/node_modules/
